  <header class="page-hero"><div class="shell"><p class="eyebrow"><span></span>Website information</p><h1>Privacy Policy</h1></div></header>
  <section class="section"><div class="shell legal"><p>Last updated: 10 July 2026</p><h2>Information you provide</h2><p>This website does not currently collect information through a website database. If you contact Kaiyu Select by email, the information you provide will be used to understand and respond to your enquiry.</p><h2>Contact form</h2><p>The contact form opens your email application and does not store your message on this website. Your email provider's privacy terms may apply.</p><h2>Website data</h2><p>Basic technical information may be processed by the website hosting provider to deliver and protect the website. No advertising trackers are intentionally included.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:contact@kaiyuselect.com.au">contact@kaiyuselect.com.au</a>.</p></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
